            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="google-rating__text">5.0 Rating on Google</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reviews-grid">
        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-card__stars">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="review-card__text">"Dr. Beyerl takes the time to truly understand what's going on. He explained everything clearly and helped me get back to running pain-free."</p>
          <p class="review-card__author">Sarah M.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-card__stars">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="review-card__text">"After years of back pain, I finally found someone who could help. The neuro rehabilitation has been life-changing for my balance."</p>
          <p class="review-card__author">Robert K.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-card__stars">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FBBF24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="review-card__text">"I appreciate that I'm not just a number here. Dr. Beyerl genuinely cares about my wellbeing and takes the time to educate me."</p>
          <p class="review-card__author">Jennifer L.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
  <section class="section section--primary">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title text-white text-center">Top Reasons to Choose The Bridge Chiropractic</h2>

      <div class="reasons-grid">
        <div class="reason-card">
          <div class="reason-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="reason-card__title">Unhurried Appointments</h3>
          <p class="reason-card__text">We take time to listen, understand your concerns, and explain what's happeningâ€”no rushed 5-minute visits.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reason-card">
          <div class="reason-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"></path><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="reason-card__title">Education First</h3>
          <p class="reason-card__text">Understand your body and why you're experiencing pain. Knowledge empowers you to take control.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reason-card">
          <div class="reason-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="reason-card__title">Proven Results</h3>
          <p class="reason-card__text">Over 500 patients helped with a 5-star Google rating. Real results from real patients you can trust.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-layout">
        <div class="faq-header">
          <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <p>Have questions about chiropractic care? We've got answers.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Ask a Question</a>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>What should I expect during my first visit?</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-item__answer">
              <p>Your first visit includes a comprehensive consultation, examination, and discussion of your health history. We'll take the time to understand your concerns and create a personalized treatment plan. Expect to spend about 45-60 minutes with us.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Is chiropractic care safe?</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-item__answer">
              <p>Yes, chiropractic care is very safe when performed by a licensed professional. Dr. Beyerl uses gentle techniques and adjusts his approach based on each patient's comfort level and health needs.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>How many visits will I need?</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-item__answer">
              <p>The number of visits varies based on your condition and goals. Some patients feel relief after just a few visits, while others benefit from ongoing wellness care. We'll discuss a recommended treatment plan during your first visit.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Do you accept insurance?</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-item__answer">
              <p>We accept most major insurance plans and can help you understand your coverage. Contact our office for specific information about your insurance plan.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Book Your Appointment Now</h2>
        <p>Take the first step toward a pain-free, active life. Schedule your consultation today.</p>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--white btn--lg">Request Appointment</a>
          <a href="tel:8582777500" class="btn btn--outline-white btn--lg">Call (858) 277-7500</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section - Split Layout */
  .hero {
    padding: 180px 0 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-off-white) 0%, var(--color-white) 100%);
  }

  .hero__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero__content h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .hero__content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    color: var(--color-gray-dark);
  }

  .hero__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero__image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
  }

  /* Services Grid */
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .service-card__icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-primary-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .service-card__title {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }

  .service-card__text {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-dark);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* About Section */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about-content p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-content .check-list {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  /* Google Rating */
  .google-rating {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  .google-rating__stars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .google-rating__text {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }

  /* Reviews Grid */
  .reviews-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .review-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .review-card__stars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .review-card__text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .review-card__author {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-gray-dark);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Why Choose Us Section */
  .section--primary {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .reasons-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .reason-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .reason-card__icon {
    width: 80px;
